Output assets/cli-demo.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Padding 15
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "budi --version"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "budi stats --period all"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "budi stats --models --period all"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "budi stats --sessions --period week"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "budi statusline --format=json"
Enter
Sleep 3s
